# Common Reusable Components (`src/components/common/`)

This directory contains components designed for reuse across different parts of the application.

- **`[SocialIcon.jsx](mdc:tibianity-frontend/src/components/common/SocialIcon.jsx)`**: Displays a social media icon link with hover effects. Used in `[Footer.jsx](mdc:tibianity-frontend/src/components/Footer.jsx)` and `[ComingSoon.jsx](mdc:tibianity-frontend/src/components/ComingSoon/ComingSoon.jsx)`.
- **`[LoginGoogleButton.jsx](mdc:tibianity-frontend/src/components/common/LoginGoogleButton.jsx)`**: Renders the standard "Login con Google" button. Includes an optional `withGradientEffect` prop to match the style of the Register button in `[Navbar.jsx](mdc:tibianity-frontend/src/components/Navbar.jsx)`.

When creating new general-purpose UI elements, consider placing them here.
